  "text": "Assuming then that we have a wanderer with the desire attempting to learn the techniques of healing while, shall I say, trapped in third density. E then, it seems to me, is primarily concerned with the balancing and unblocking of energy centers. Am I correct in this assumption? I am Ra. This is correct only insofar as the healer has become balanced. May it be a channel for the balancing of and other self. The healing is first practiced upon the self, if we may say this in another way.",
